name: Jelly Jess is Jumping!
description:
This is a game is where you jump on objects this game will lag on low end PCS.

This is a game based on a jelly YouTuber.

This a game based on nothing

To play the game without a ray tracing GPU

  • Operating System: 64-bit Windows 7, Windows 8.1, Windows 10.
  • Processor: Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300.
  • Memory: 4 GB RAM.
  • Graphics: NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 2GB
  • DirectX: Version 11
  • Storage: 1GB

This is for RTX Mode

  • Operating System: 64-bit Windows 10.
  • Processor: Intel i3-3220 or AMD Equivalent
  • Memory: 8 GB RAM.
  • Graphics: NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2060 6GB
  • DirectX: Version 11
  • Storage: 1GB

To esc this game you press F11 and press the X on the top right on your screen!
